                  color: Color(0xFFF3F3F2),
                ),
              ),
              const SizedBox(height: 8),
              Wrap(
                spacing: 8,
                runSpacing: 8,
                children: MarqueeSelectionMode.values.map((mode) {
                  final bool selected = _marqueeMode == mode;
                  return _MarqueeModeIconButton(
                    icon: mode.icon,
